title: ILinearPatternFeatureData.D2EndSeedReference
description: Gets or sets the seed feature geometry to offset from the up-to reference geometry in Direction 2 of this bidirectional linear pattern feature.
returns: Seed geometry ( vertex , edge , face , or plane ) to offset from ILinearPatternFeatureData::D2EndReference
remarks:
This property is valid only if
ILinearPatternFeatureData::D2EndCondition
is set to
swPatternEndCondition_e
.swPatternEndCondition_UpToReference.
